50|$|American Society of Muslims: in {{an attempt}} to bring the teachings of the Nation of Islam more in line with <b>mainstream</b> Sunni <b>Islam,</b> Warith Deen Mohammed {{established}} the American Society of Muslims in 1975. This offshoot wanted to bring its teachings more in line with <b>mainstream</b> Sunni <b>Islam,</b> establishing mosques instead of temples and promoting the Five pillars of Islam.|$|R
